post_text: The following video from the BBC shows the obstacles facing Southside ISD families during the COVID-19 pandemic. It has been seen around the world.
shared_text:
BBC News posted an episode of BBC's Cut Through the Noise.
September 10 at 3:35 PM ·

No school desk. No toilet. A failing WiFi connection.

“As a parent, you gotta do what you gotta do. If it means coming to sit by a school bus all day, that’s what we gotta do.”

The Gould family now spends 8 hours a day doing school work in their car. Along with millions of children without the internet at home they have to seek alternatives for remote education during the pandemic.

This is what it’s like. #CutThroughTheNoise
text:
The following video from the BBC shows the obstacles facing Southside ISD families during the COVID-19 pandemic. It has been seen around the world.

BBC News posted an episode of BBC's Cut Through the Noise.
September 10 at 3:35 PM ·

No school desk. No toilet. A failing WiFi connection.

“As a parent, you gotta do what you gotta do. If it means coming to sit by a school bus all day, that’s what we gotta do.”

The Gould family now spends 8 hours a day doing school work in their car. Along with millions of children without the internet at home they have to seek alternatives for remote education during the pandemic.

This is what it’s like. #CutThroughTheNoise

Hot Spot Information – Wait List | Southside Independent School District
text:
Please fill out this form to be put on the SISD waitlist for an internet hotspot. When the hotspots arrive in district you will be contacted in the order your request has been received. After you fill out this order request, it will be reviewed and processed based on the availability of the devices. Southside ISD will issue one per household for student use. [ 53 more words ]
